<channel|>Here is a list of locations from original vanilla World of Warcraft for every letter of the alphabet:

**A** - Azeroth
**B** - Brackenwall Village
**C** - Crossroads
**D** - Dustwallow Marsh
**E** - Elwynn Forest
**F** - Felwood
**G** - Gadgetzan
**H** - Hinterlands
**I** - Ironforge
**J** - Jadefire Hollow
**K** - Karazhan (The tower is visible/accessible in vanilla)
**L** - Loch Modan
**M** - Moonglade
**N** - Northshire Abbey
**O** - Onyxia's Lair
**P** - Putresss's Lab
**Q** - Questing Hubs (or Quicksand Basin)
**R** - Ratchet
**S** - Stormwind
**T** - Thousand Needles
**U** - Undercity
**V** - Valley of Trials
**W** - Winterspring
**X** - Xavius's domain (The Naxxramas area, though the raid is later, the lore/presence is established)
**Y** - Ysaril's Grove
**Z** - Zul'Gurub [end of text]


